></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2><span class=\"block font-display tracking-tight text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] [text-wrap:balance] text-2xl font-semibold\">More projects</span></h2></div></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 mt-16\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-start pl-8 relative before:absolute after:absolute before:bg-[var(--theme-text-muted)] after:bg-[var(--theme-border-subtle)] before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-6 before:w-px after:top-8 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-px\"><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">Portfolio Site Modernization</h3><time dateTime=\"2026\" class=\"order-first text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">2026</time><p class=\"mt-2.5 text-base text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">Rebuilt my portfolio from a static AWS-hosted resume into a modern Next.js 15 site with Tailwind CSS v4, MDX content pipeline, Pagefind search, dark/light theme, PWA support, and Cloudflare Pages deployment.</p><a class=\"mt-6 flex gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\" aria-label=\"Read more: Portfolio Site Modernization\" href=\"/projects/portfolio-site\">Read more<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute inset-0\"></span></a></div></article></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><article><div class=\"relative flex flex-col items-start pl-8 relative before:absolute after:absolute before:bg-[var(--theme-text-muted)] after:bg-[var(--theme-border-subtle)] before:top-0 before:left-0 before:h-6 before:w-px after:top-8 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-px\"><h3 class=\"mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">Azure Web Store on Kubernetes</h3><time dateTime=\"2024\" class=\"order-first text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">2024</time><p class=\"mt-2.5 text-base text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\">Microservices web store on AKS — Java Spring Boot services, Azure B2C identity, API Management gateway, and GitHub Actions CI/CD.</p><a class=\"mt-6 flex gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--theme-text-primary)] transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\" aria-label=\"Read more: Azure Web Store on Kubernetes\" href=\"/projects/azure-kubernetes-store\">Read more<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"w-6 flex-none fill-current\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M24 3 18 .5v2H0v1h18v2L24 3Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"absolute inset-0\"></span></a></div></article></div></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 mt-12 w-full sm:mt-16 lg:mt-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-x-12 gap-y-8\"><nav><div class=\"font-display text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\">Site Map</div><ul role=\"list\" class=\"mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 text-sm text-[var(--theme-text-secondary)]\"><li class=\"mt-2\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"mt-2\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"mt-2\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"mt-2\"><a class=\"transition hover:text-[var(--theme-text-primary)]\" href=\"/projects\">Project